<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cambiar Contrase√±a - LogiCo</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .recover-container { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; padding: 20px; }
        .recover-card {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease;
        }
        .recover-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .logo-icon { font-size: 3em; margin-bottom: 15px; display: block; }
        .recover-header h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f13ec, #087ed3);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .recover-header p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .messages { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .alert {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .alert-error {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
            color: #fca5a5;
        }
        .alert-success {
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
            color: #86efac;
        }
        .form-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .form-group label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .form-group input {
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            font-size: 0.95em;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            color: white;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .form-group input::placeholder { color: #64748b; }
        .form-group input:focus {
            outline: none;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-color: rgba(15, 19, 236, 0.5);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15, 19, 236, 0.2);
        }
        .info-box {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 14px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: #93c5fd;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .recover-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f13ec, #087ed3);
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(15, 19, 236, 0.3);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .recover-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            filter: brightness(1.15);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(15, 19, 236, 0.4);
        }
        .back-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            color: #0f13ec;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(15, 19, 236, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(15, 19, 236, 0.3);
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            width: fit-content;
        }
        .back-btn:hover { background: rgba(15, 19, 236, 0.2); }
        .password-req {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            margin-top: 8px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="recover-container">
        <div class="recover-card">
            <a href="{% url 'recuperar_password' %}" class="back-btn">‚Üê Volver</a>
            <div class="recover-header">
                <span class="logo-icon">üîë</span>
                <h1>Nueva Contrase√±a</h1>
                <p>Establece una contrase√±a segura</p>
            </div>

            {% if messages %}
                <div class="messages">
                    {% for message in messages %}
                        <div class="alert {% if message.tags %}alert-{{ message.tags }}{% endif %}">
                            {{ message }}
                        </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="info-box">
                üîí M√≠nimo 8 caracteres. Usa may√∫sculas, min√∫sculas, n√∫meros y s√≠mbolos.
            </div>

            <form method="POST">
                {% csrf_token %}
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password1">Nueva Contrase√±a</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password1" name="password1" 
                           placeholder="Contrase√±a segura" required>
                    <div class="password-req">
                        ‚úì M√≠nimo 8 caracteres
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password2">Confirmar Contrase√±a</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password2" name="password2" 
                           placeholder="Confirma tu contrase√±a" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="recover-btn">üîê Guardar Contrase√±a</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>